			<p>BAYADA Home Health Care, then called RN Home Care, was born out of Mark Baiada’s vision of helping people live at home safely with comfort, independence and dignity. The company began in Philadelphia, PA, where Mark Baiada, Founder and President, opened its first office in 1975.</p>

			<p>Merely four decades later, we have grown from those humble beginnings to become a national leader in the home care industry, with 298 offices in 23 states. The number of people helped by BAYADA Home Health Care continues to grow, with our primary belief always remaining the same: our clients come first. It’s <span class="italics">The BAYADA Way</span>.</p>

			<p><span class="italics">The BAYADA Way</span> expresses what is most critical to our work. It defines our mission and Mark’s vision for the future. It states our beliefs and the fundamental values that guide our work...Compassion, Excellence, and Reliability.</p>

